title: Gamma ray yields from proton bombardment of B-10.

x4freetext: Gamma ray yields from proton bombardment of B-10.
Proton beam is 0.5 mu-A.
An enriched (99.8%) B-10 target, 675 mu-g/cm thick
deposited on a thick tantalum backing was used.
